I am not a big gamer, but this one really gets me hooked. You have to create a lot of skill for handling these different cars in the race ... Bronze, Silver and Gold gets you to certain start positions and then you really got to optimize your steering/drifting and gas pedal controls to get ahead of the race in various different race tracks with different directions. You can also just improve your lap time and drive around your own cars image from the previous round and best round, which teaches you a lot of techniques that make you go faster. It runs perfectly on my good old Nexus S (single core CPU) on Ice Cream Sandwich (Anroid 4.0) without any visual stutter, great frame rates, but it really lets the CPU run with max speed, which drains your battery in a way you could never imagine. I have no experience with the online mode yet, but even the offline mode is so much fun, that I don't miss anything. Big thanks you to the developers for releasing this fun package for such a low price - amazing work!
